### 6.1 macOS vs Windows Scroll Direction

| Platform | Default Scroll Direction |
|----------|--------------------------|
| macOS (trackpad) | "Natural" (content follows fingers) |
| macOS (mouse) | Same as trackpad (unless changed) |
| Windows | "Traditional" (opposite of macOS) |
| Linux | Varies by desktop environment |

